{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_13_01_short",
  "title": "井川葵 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『地下闘技場最強アイドルトーナメント』後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……。……うん、いい感じだ\n後もう少し、ターンを速くすれば……もっと……",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}君、どうしたの？　さっきから\n隅っこで突っ立ってるけど、じっと見てるだけ？",
      "startTime": 16.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕としては、新しいステップの感想を\n聞かせてほしいんだけど",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵の練習する姿が、あまりに熱心だったから\n邪魔をしたくなかったんだ。お疲れ様、葵",
      "startTime": 28.2602171246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、新しいステップの感想だけど……\n俺の目には完璧に見えたよ。百点だと思う",
      "startTime": 36.1015867551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。僕としてはまだ八十点くらいかな\nターンに入るタイミングがまだ甘いよ",
      "startTime": 45.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今の時点で八十点なら十分じゃないか\n相変わらず自分に厳しいな、葵は",
      "startTime": 52.6538086255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう少し軽めの練習でもいいと思うけどな\n追い込み方が、まるで本番直前みたいなハードさだぞ",
      "startTime": 60.1204752922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n本番直前だよ。明日が本番なんだから",
      "startTime": 65.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}